Subject: [PATCH v17 09/19] ARM: dts: n900: Add reg property to the LP5523 channel node
Date:   Thu, 14 Nov 2019 07:30:13 -0600
Message-ID: <20191114133023.32185-10-dmurphy@ti.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.22.0.214.g8dca754b1e
In-Reply-To: <20191114133023.32185-1-dmurphy@ti.com>
